org.codehaus.mojo.jaxws

Class TestWsImportMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • org.codehaus.mojo.jaxws.TestWsImportMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    @Mojo(name="wsimport-test",
      defaultPhase=GENERATE_TEST_SOURCES,
      requiresDependencyResolution=TEST)
public class TestWsImportMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Parses wsdl and binding files and generates Java code needed to access it (for tests).

    ${maven.test.skip} property is honored. If it is set, code generation is skipped.

    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi
